high_descs: Make a right around the couches towards the tall lamp.
Pick up the keys next to the lamp.
Turn the power off of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the keys near the lamp to turn it off.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the table, and walk to the small round table on the right.
Pick up the set of keys on the left side of the table.
Turn left and walk to the tall lamp on the right.
Turn off the tall lamp next to the small table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a set of keys by the lack of light from a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the sofa on the right to the small black round end table next to the lamp.
Pick up the keys on the left side of the end table.
Move over left to the lamp.
Turn off the lamp and look at the keys.
anns.task_desc: Look at the keys with lamp turned off.
